title: S5 Jung/Supp - Looking for Solo Q DUO partner
body: Hey, I've found that when I play ranked in Solo Que on my own I tend to lose more often but when I have a partner it's easier to communicate and carry matches. At the moment I'm running through the guides in lolpro and skillcapped and always improving. If you're looking for a duo partner send me a request.

replies.body: I am G5. AD Main. Would be keen if you are. As long as you're not a rager. Ranked but fun ranked games im looking for. nothing too serious
feel you it i get bored, main/top/supp add me if you want thorneka3
hey I'm s5 too wanna duo ?
